5c1d95e397e98c2e49130fe40040.mp4?t=1686430265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Fight hordes of evil Karen minions, from expired coupon launchers to angry coffee cups across six different environments.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152760/extras/b69b2405e6ace6d20f5f4d2a823d873c.poster.avif?t=1686430265\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152760/extras/b69b2405e6ace6d20f5f4d2a823d873c.webm?t=1686430265\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2152760/extras/b69b2405e6ace6d20f5f4d2a823d873c.mp4?t=1686430265\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Grow more powerful every run by spending your hard earned modules on stat and weapon upgrades. <br><br><strong>Full game features: </strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over <strong>50 in-game upgrades</strong> for tons of different build options</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over <strong>20 meta progression upgrades</strong> to get stronger every run</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>4 epic Karen bosses</strong> to destroy</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>6 different areas</strong> to defend</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Fully voiced dialogue</strong> for your wing mate Amanda and the four Karens</li></ul>",
